{"type": "article", "id": 14519, "title": "无印良品在东京开了全球最大旗舰店，拿一万本书做装饰", "description": "这是无印良品单体面积最大的店铺了，另外，他们还在东京开了一家书店。", "date": "2015-09-06T12:59:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7137, "name": "东京"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 15579, "name": "MUJI Books"}, {"id": 303, "name": "无印良品"}, {"id": 264, "name": "MUJI"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 146, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115418lOPAf4UNLGerIVJt.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t今年的 9 月 4 号，<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2015/09/04/10000-books-line-a-bookshelf-that-traverses-the-new-muji-store-in-tokyo/\" target=\"_blank\">无印良品在东京的 Yurakucho 开出了一家新店</a>，这家“新店”是由原先的旧店翻新而成的。它共有 3 层，面积为 3277 平方米，是目前为止世界上最大的 MUJI 旗舰店。店内<span>最亮眼的要属书架装置了，</span><span>1 </span><span>万本书被罗列在这个大家伙上，从一层蔓延到二层空间。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115414IhOfDg5cbUuLrtvp.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"442\" title=\"9 月 4 日，无印良品最大面积店铺在东京开幕\" alt=\"9 月 4 日，无印良品最大面积店铺在东京开幕\" data-ratio=\"0.690625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>9 月 4 日，无印良品最大面积店铺在东京开幕</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115415nPQtj9uiFkNbp2wJ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"庞大的书架从一楼延伸至二楼\" alt=\"庞大的书架从一楼延伸至二楼\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>庞大的书架从一楼延伸至二楼</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115415irSLGCJ0FmvUKBpE.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"853\" title=\"书架上放置着 1 万本书\" alt=\"书架上放置着 1 万本书\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>书架上放置着 1 万本书</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021154169vL7ixIRk6hK2Tqj.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"853\" title=\"细节\" alt=\"细节\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>细节</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115416xyLMNrzecsfdPZkB.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"书架装置\" alt=\"书架装置\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>书架装置</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这个书架是无印良品邀请建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.bow-wow.jp/\">Atelier Bow\r\nWow</a> 特别定制的，这家设计事务所已有 20 多年的历史，他们设计了不少木结构的建筑。<span>此前，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/muji-books/\" target=\"_blank\">无印良品还在九州福冈市的 </a></span><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/muji-books/\" target=\"_blank\">canal city <span>开出了首家书店</span></a><span>，书店里陈列了超过三万本书籍，这是无印良品初涉书店业务。在这家书店中，书的分类方式很特别，有一个专门的类别叫“同级生的书”，你可以看到同龄人都在读什么。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115417eqV207r5F1tbRf83.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"MUJI Books\" alt=\"MUJI Books\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>MUJI Books</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115417vJIDjumP8nq12l3A.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"MUJI Books\" alt=\"MUJI Books\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>MUJI Books</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115417Qn2b0lCEWe1FNx9c.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"MUJI Books\" alt=\"MUJI Books\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>MUJI Books</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115418pvzr08BEIGhVliy7.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"MUJI Books\" alt=\"MUJI Books\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>MUJI Books</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2015/09/04/10000-books-line-a-bookshelf-that-traverses-the-new-muji-store-in-tokyo/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>spoon-tamago</em><em></em></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}